summary: Can I just say I love how muh positive attention Detective Pikachu is getting?
body:
Can I just say I love how muh positive attention Detective Pikachu is getting?

Honestly, after having played the game and seeing that the game didn’t nessesarily have that huge of a reception (in comparison to like a main Pokemon title game), I was really nervous for the movie when I first heard the news. I freaking loved the game, and I’m so glad other people get to experience the same general storyline. ♡
